        <updateDate>2008-05-03T13:56:08Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Supporting Emergency Responders Volunteer Efforts Act of 2008 or the SERVE Act of 2008 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow a $1,000 refundable tax credit for individuals who are bona fide volunteer members of a qualified volunteer fire department who provide firefighting, ambulance, or emergency medical services.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
